Data Structure
================

User
  has_one :portfolio
  has_many :pieces, through :portfolio
  
  first_name (string)
  last_name (string)
  login (string) *unique
  email (string)
  password (string)
  password_confirmation (string)
  account_tier (integer [1, 2, 3])
  about_me (text)
  tag_line (string)
  avatar (image)
  design_type (integer [1, 2]) [1=editing css with forms, 2=edit css directly]
  layout_type (integer [1, 2]) [1=grid, 2=list]
  
Portfolio
  belongs_to :user
  has_many :pieces
  
Piece
  belongs_to :user
  belongs_to :portfolio
  
  title (string)
  description (string)
  price (decimal)
  for_sale (boolean)
  image1 (image)
  image2 (image)
  image3 (image)
  image4 (image)
  image5 (image)
  

Account Tiers
=================

5 pieces, 1 image each
then
the paid accounts are 15 pieces, 5 images each
and
25 pieces, 5 images each


Image Sizing
===============

Small Thumb: 70x70
Large Thumb: 116x116
View Size: max width of 710, 400 height
